Product Description

Premium keycaps, without smashing your wallet.

The Glorious Aura Keycap set is a one of a kind keycap set which harnesses the beauty of your keyboards LED's and creates a unique look and feel that will definitely capture anyone's attention.

Every piece is made of high-quality PBT plastic which brings a premium typing experience and lasts much longer than ABS keycaps. The Aura keycaps have milky transparent legends and sides which creates a vibrant, yet soft, glow around your keyboard when your keyboards LED are turned on.

The Glorious Aura Keycaps will definitely capture the attention of anyone around you and is the ultimate keycap set to ascend your battlestation to the next level.

Enjoy countless hours of gaming as the keys are designed to last and will never wear out over time.

Pair up these keycaps with our Glorious Modular Mechanical Keyboard (GMMK) for the ultimate typing, and gaming experience.

Features:

  • Standard 104 Keys (ANSI-US / QWERTY Layout)
  • Colors: Black
  • Cherry-MX / Gateron / Kailh + stem compatible
  • Compatible with any mechanical keyboard with standard bottom row (fits Full Size, Tenkeyless, Compact layouts).
  • PBT Plastic
  • Double Shot Injection Legends 
  • Backlight LED compatible (Transparent legends)
  • Standard Bottom Row
  • Key sizes in the CTRL / ALT / WINDOWS / SPACEBAR / etc row are (from left to right are) 1.25 1.25 1.25 spacebar(6.25X) 1.25 1.25 1.25 1.25
  • Comes with 1 extra Glorious ASCEND ESC key and regular Aura Esc key



Transparent Keycaps that amplifies your keyboards RGB

Show off your keyboard in style.

Durable double shot PBT material

Ready to last through all your intense gaming sessions. Our strong PBT plastic keycaps will outlive your keyboard!

Compatible with Glorious GMMK

This keycap set is fully compatible with our Glorious Modular Mechanical Keyboard (GMMK).

How does Amazon calculate star ratings?
Amazon calculates a product’s star ratings based on a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The model takes into account factors including the age of a rating, whether the ratings are from verified purchasers, and factors that establish reviewer trustworthiness.

Alexander
5.0 out of 5 stars They are built for Cherry, Gateron, and Kailh keys.
Reviewed in the United States on April 1, 2019
Color: Aura (Black)Verified Purchase
These keys are awesome! I put them on my Corsair Strafe RGB keyboard. My colors I have on my keyboard look so much brighter and cooler thanks to the keys being translucent! I was using the keys as I was typing this review. However, my only gripe with these keys is that the spacebar was too short to mount to the stabilizers, as well as the windows, function, and the key that functions as another right click did not fit because they were too big and there was not enough room for the keys to mount properly, since they are wider than a normal key. Overall, I am very satisfied with the keycap set, in spite of the fitting issue.

tanigooch
4.0 out of 5 stars awesome product, but make sure all keycaps will fit
Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2019
Color: Aura (Black)Verified Purchase
Pudding keycaps to give your RGB keyboard the awesome glow effect they deserve! Really makes your keyboard stand out with the backlighting and gives it a really nice effect. The only problem I encountered was that the space bar, function (fn) and command button (Cmnd) keycaps didn't fit on my keyboard. The stabilizer holes on the space bar didn't match up with my original, so when you put the stabilizers on the pudding cap, it wouldn't seat right. The function and commond keycaps were too large and didn't fit the layout. Would have needed the size keycaps for the letters instead and it would have been a perfect fit. Also, when putting the stabilizers on the backspace key, it changed the keystroke feel so badly that II had to take the stabilizers off the backspace key and it fixed the response issue. Other than that, they keycaps look great and feel pretty good too. I'm currently using a Razer Huntsman Elite Keyboard. Good product, good quality, just not 100% compatibility. 4 stars.
